Love is what i dream of hoping to find myself in
 love is what keep me going in life.
 
sometimes i dream of falling 
in love with one special boy 
a boy who would love me for me

dreams of love from another to
feel love send me into a land of hopes that
one day i would find that one true boy

i waited all my life for this
love to feel this love and
on this day where the sun was in the sky
shining so bright my love finally i met
the special boy, i finally know was love is
i finally felt the power of love.

Love is the deadest sin of all it can bring out the worst in us. 
     Love is brought on ,when you feel something for that some one which only ends up in betrayal and death. Love  is like a red rose you give to someone which sooner or later turnes to black and peel away , love can bring out our dark side and be the death of us.
